snippet.title: The G.O.A.T.S Podcast: Ft Canelo Alvarez, Terence Crawford, Tom Brady, Shaquille O’Neal & Dana White
snippet.description:
They’ve done it all. Now they’re talking about what it really means to be the best 🔥

Listen to the G.O.A.TS Podcast ahead of Canelo Alvarez vs Terence Crawford, both fighters sat down with Promoter Dana White as well as 2 Greats in the sporting world with Tom Brady and Shaquille O'Neal. 

#CaneloAlvarez #TomBrady #TerenceCrawford 

0:00 Intro
0:50 Does Crawford Have Power to Beat Canelo?
1:15 Canelo Thoughts on Crawford Reach
1:50 How Does Canelo Beat Crawford?
2:05 Thoughts on The Fight?
2:55 Dana White Thoughts
4:35 Tom Brady Thoughts
5:20 How Does Crawford Want To Win?
7:33 How Does Canelo Want To Win?
8:15 Canelo & Crawford Back and Forth On Resume
11:00 Animosity Between Them
12:02 Where's Does The Fight Rank?
12:43 Training Camp
13:50 Handling Power
15:51 Crawford Fight Instead Of Benavidez
16:40 What Does GOAT Mean?
19:20 Closing Convo
